7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 eztoc-toggle-hide-by-default' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-become-a-psychiatrist-in-canada\/#Tuition_Fee_to_become_a_Psychiatrist\" title=\"Tuition Fee to become a Psychiatrist\">Tuition Fee to become a Psychiatrist<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-become-a-psychiatrist-in-canada\/#Requirements_for_Becoming_a_Psychiatrist\" title=\"Requirements for Becoming a Psychiatrist\">Requirements for Becoming a Psychiatrist<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-become-a-psychiatrist-in-canada\/#Eligibility_to_Become_a_Psychiatrist\" title=\"Eligibility to Become a Psychiatrist\">Eligibility to Become a Psychiatrist<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-become-a-psychiatrist-in-canada\/#Average_Psychiatrist_Salary_in_Canada\" title=\"Average Psychiatrist Salary in Canada\">Average Psychiatrist Salary in Canada<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-become-a-psychiatrist-in-canada\/#How_to_Become_a_Psychiatrist_How_to_Become_a_Psychiatrist_in_Canada\" title=\"How to Become a Psychiatrist| How to Become a Psychiatrist in Canada\">How to Become a Psychiatrist| How to Become a Psychiatrist in Canada<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>The process of becoming a psychiatrist can be considered stressful and hard, which you will need to invest a lot of time and effort into your education; you will be enlightened on the take to become one \u00a0<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-2071 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/holistic-health-coach-stocksy-studio-firma-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p><strong>Contents<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82179069\">Tuition Fee to become a Psychiatrist<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82179070\">Requirements for Becoming a Psychiatrist<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82179071\">Eligibility to Become a Psychiatrist<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82179072\">Average Psychiatrist Salary in Canada<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc82179073\">How to Become a Psychiatrist<\/a><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"tuition-fee-to-become-a-psychiatrist\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tuition_Fee_to_become_a_Psychiatrist\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82179069\"><\/a>Tuition Fee to become a Psychiatrist<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>The total cost to become a psychiatrist is different depending on the province or the area you school students who attend public colleges to spend about \u00a0$23,890 intuition, and student fees, which can do not include the cost of books, etc.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"requirements-for-becoming-a-psychiatrist\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Requirements_for_Becoming_a_Psychiatrist\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82179070\"><\/a>Requirements for Becoming a Psychiatrist<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong><em>To become a psychiatrist you will need the below outline requirements which are as follows:<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>A five-year degree in medicine must be recognized by the General Medical Council<\/li>\n<li>Foundation program of two-year general training<\/li>\n<li>Three years of core training in psychiatry<\/li>\n<li>Specialty training of three years.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"eligibility-to-become-a-psychiatrist\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Eligibility_to_Become_a_Psychiatrist\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82179071\"><\/a>Eligibility to Become a Psychiatrist<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>To become a psychiatrist as an upcoming student you need to complete an MBBS degree and then either enroll in an MD course in Psychiatry or Diploma in Psychiatry.<\/li>\n<li>You must complete the class of 12<sup>th<\/sup> with science stream with Biology as one of the main subjects.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"average-psychiatrist-salary-in-canada\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Average_Psychiatrist_Salary_in_Canada\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82179072\"><\/a>Average Psychiatrist Salary in Canada<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>The salary for a psychiatrist is $241,715 per year or $124 per hour.<\/li>\n<li>And in Entry-level positions start at $162,639 per year<\/li>\n<li>The most experienced workers earn up to $348,000 per year.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-become-a-psychiatrist-how-to-become-a-psychiatrist-in-canada\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_Become_a_Psychiatrist_How_to_Become_a_Psychiatrist_in_Canada\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc82179073\"><\/a>How to Become a Psychiatrist| How to Become a Psychiatrist in Canada<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Take MCAT<\/li>\n<li>Apply and be accepted in medical school<\/li>\n<li>Graduate College<\/li>\n<li><strong>Complete a psychiatric residency<\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong>Become board-certified with the American Board of Psychiatry and Neurology<\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong>Apply to be a licensed doctor<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>See also &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; <a title=\"UK medical School Requirements 2024\" href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/uk-medical-school-requirements\/\" rel=\"bookmark nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">UK medical School Requirements 2024<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"ex